0.dialouge:
Yoo!~ You Two!~
You guys are from Athier Peek right? I never thought I'd get me meet the bigshots.

1.dialouge: I hope your shard collecting has been going.

2.dialouge: Because I have a little...~ proposal.

3.dialouge: I've got a lil proposal for you.

4.dialouge: Sorry we're kinda in a hurry.

5.dialouge: I'll make it quick.~ Your time is oh so valuable after all.

6.dialouge:
You see... We've all got a quota of shards to collect.~
But some of us are a little short on luck.

7.dialouge: Sooo... I was thinking that it would be great if we worked out something that would help all of us..

8.dialouge: How about you guys just turn back and let me handle this area.

9.dialouge: I'll look for shards around here, you guys keep looking there.

10.dialouge:
Yeah about that...~
I don't think there are that many shards left there.

11.dialouge:
Have you tried looking a little past the lodgings.~
There might be a few more there.

12.dialouge: No.. But that's a little far from here isn't it.

13.dialouge: I know I know...~ I'd would really be a huge favor for everyone. Vanguards are supposed to work together after all aren't they?

15.dialouge: Come on man!~ Take one for the team will you?

16.dialouge:
He's kinda got a point Klay.~
 The team would certainly-

17.dialouge: But we aren't a team Malo!

18.dialouge: How would splitting up help us?

20.dialouge: Well...~ It's not like I expect big shots like you two to understand anyways.

21.dialouge: Well...~ It's not like I expect big shots like you two to understand anyways.

22.dialouge: You two may cutout for the selection... but you two aren't cutout to vanguards.
